          <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> â€º <a href="/allmybooks" title="All current and future books by Mary">All Mary&#039;s Books</a></div>                              <h2>Historical Romances</h2>                                                  <div class="clear-block">
            <div id="node-17" class="node">



  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <p>Published by Harlequin Mills &amp; Boon</p>
<p>The books have all been published in hardback, paperback and most of them, in large print. Many have been translated into foreign languages and also reprinted in Omnibus editions and collections. Most of them are also available as ebooks. &nbsp;Click on the links for Mills &amp; Boon or Harlequin for availability and to buy. Those I have republished as ebooks myself can be found in a separate list under All my Books in the left hand column.</p>
